<span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">E</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.275em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">W</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">D</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: -0.18em; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">N</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mrow MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size4-R" style="padding-top: 1.551em; padding-bottom: 1.551em;">[</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">E</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.275em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.014em;">Q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">Y</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">X</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mrow MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size4-R" style="padding-top: 1.551em; padding-bottom: 1.551em;">[</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">log</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 3.988em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="width: 3.988em; top: -1.59em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em; padding-right: 0.014em;">q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="width: 3.988em; bottom: -1.09em;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">|</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">，</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 3.988em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.68em; vertical-align: -1.09em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size4-R" style="padding-top: 1.551em; padding-bottom: 1.551em;">]</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size4-R" style="padding-top: 1.551em; padding-bottom: 1.551em;">]</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">。</span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>对给定模型进行预测并根据后验进行采样是非共同的 - 不可能在不改变结果的情况下将期望值进出上述对数。因此，我们得到了两种预测方法和两种不同类型的概括误差。</p><h1>边界概括</h1><p>当得出概括界限时，我们不仅必须决定<i>哪种</i>概括度量指标，还必须决定<i>如何</i>绑定它。有三个主要决定：</p><ol><li> <strong>“全球”还是“本地”</strong> ？您是否希望结果保持整个重量或特定的权重选择？</li><li><strong>数据集依赖性还是无关</strong>？您是否希望将结果保留为您的特定样本或数据集的所有可能选择？</li><li><strong>统一，平均或概率</strong>？您是否希望义务始终保持，平均或最小概率？</li></ol><h2>全球与本地</h2><p>第一个也是最重要的问题是是在整个模型类中还是仅在特定模型上绑定概括误差。古典学习理论采用全球方法。现代深度学习理论采用了更本地的方法。奇异学习理论提出了第三种<i>介绍</i>方法，该方法获得了模型<i>子类</i>的概括界限。</p><p><strong>全球界限</strong>。全球方法是一种最糟糕的方法。上限必须适合所有型号，因此它仅与您最糟糕的一般型号一样紧。发现这些最坏的情况通常涉及询问模型类如何适合随机噪声。在纯粹的随机噪声上训练的模型根本无法概括，因为没有信号，因此拟合随机噪声完全意味着最坏的概括误差是可怕的。这将概括变成了表达性问题，该问题由<strong>VC维度</strong>， <strong>Rademacher复杂性</strong>和<strong>覆盖数</strong>等复杂性指标（如复杂度指标）进行操作。</p><p>由于神经网络通常可以完美地拟合噪声，因此根据这些措施，它们高度复杂，并且最终的界限变得<strong>空虚</strong>：它们微不足道地预测测试误差将小于100％。</p><p>我们在实践中观察到良好的概括的原因是，并非类中的所有模型都同样复杂。例如，避免权重的成功表明，许多权重可以安全地设置为零并消除。因此，平均概括可能与最坏情况泛化大不相同。</p><p><strong>本地边界</strong>。您可以不用研究模型类表达噪声的能力，而可以研究特定模型对噪声的鲁棒性，而是将噪声应用于输入（<strong>边距理论</strong>），噪声应用于重量（<strong>最小清晰度/平坦</strong>，<strong>压缩理论</strong>）或应用于训练样本（<strong>算法稳定性和鲁棒性</strong>）的噪声。为了获得概括，可以将这些类型的经验鲁棒性交换为预测的鲁棒性，以兑现新数据。</p><p>尽管这些结果导致了实际的改进，但边界仍然太松散了，无法解释大型现实世界模型。即使对于MNIST，测试误差的最佳上限也比我们在最新模型中实际观察到的数量级大。进步最终会赶上，还是这些限制反映了这种方法更根本的问题？ </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/zcguehgktxwepa6ylikb" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/efyd9xzpcdjmx05jlseb 210w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/a2ofnleq15kjargchgmh 420w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/ugo81wjk4n6nxoulbblw 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/hxsnbqp4ldn6hfyvqae8 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/kr6ltjzyetq5hsuldfx0 1050w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/xqo62hjjuuzuvoywhkx2 1260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/cxm5y7aofeis5kz3tyzm 1470w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/tokkmeudmmal1nds3hr9 1680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/ugq9wq6deknfzmljmgz5 1890w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/zljtbpcixzhx3vgjml7c 2032w"><figcaption>来自<a href="https://proceedings.neurips.cc/paper_files/paper/2022/hash/cbeec55c50c3367024bafab2438a021b-Abstract-Conference.html">Lotfi等人。 （2022）“ Pac-bayes压缩界限如此紧密，以至于可以解释概括”</a> ：分类误差（较低=更好）的这些界限或多或少是最新的。星星<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\star"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">指示</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>使用数据依赖性先验（见下文）。尽管这些界限中的某些范围是非易变的（即比100％更高），但它们仍然远非有意义地约束大型现实世界系统。还有很多概括要解释。</figcaption></figure><p><strong>介质边界</strong>。您可以研究学习模型的<i>分布</i>对噪声的反应方式，而不是研究<i>单个</i>模型对噪声的反应。随着视角的改变，研究概括变成了比较模型<i>子类</i>的问题。</p><p>在深度学习理论的领域中，这种观点已经隐含了，这些领域获得了涉及<strong>体重规范</strong>，<strong>压缩</strong>，<strong>最小清晰度/平坦性</strong>和各种<strong>信息理论量的</strong>概括界限。它在奇异学习理论中是明确的，该理论提出了一组规范的可观察物，用于研究模型的复杂性和概括，例如<strong>学习系数</strong>，<strong>奇异的波动</strong>和<strong>多重性</strong>。对于理想化的贝叶斯学习者，SLT预测了大数据限制中贝叶斯和吉布斯概括误差的<i>值</i>（不仅是上限）。</p><h2>数据集依赖性</h2><p>第二个问题是要限制给定数据集的概括错误还是在可能的数据集的整个分布之间。实际上，我们只有一个数据集，并且想了解该特定数据集的模型将如何推广。从理论上讲，通常更容易将依赖性的依赖性边缘化。</p><p>边缘化数据集通常是合理的，理由是我们对模型在大量数据的限制中的执行更感兴趣。在这些范围内，任何单个数据点的影响都会消失。但是，在分布具有像RL之类的尾巴的情况下，这种假设可能不会存在。</p><h2>概括范围的口味</h2><p>最后一个问题主要是美学：我们如何打扮自己的界限？由于概括是由数据和权重组成的，因此将其分为两个子问题：如何打扮绑定的数据以及如何打扮重量的绑定？</p><p><strong>统一边界</strong>。最强的界限是在模型类中<i>均匀地</i>保持的界限，即涉及通用量化符的界限：</p> <span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="G_n(f_w) < \epsilon,\quad \forall w\in\mathcal W"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">g</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">，</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 1em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∀w∈W</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">_</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-cal-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em; padding-right: 0.046em;">_</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>这是相对于<i>权重</i>定义的，因为我们很少对在数据集上均匀保持的界限感兴趣。除了微不足道的分布外，总有病理学的数据会表现出较差的概括。</p><p><strong>概率边界。</strong>较弱（从某种意义上说，它们并不总是存在），但是通常更紧密（上限是下限）是“概率”的界限：</p> <span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbb P(G_n(f_w) < \epsilon) > 1-\delta."><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">p</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">g</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">>;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">-δ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.007em;">。</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">_</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>尽管一个人可以相对于权重的分布制定概率绑定，但实际上，这些界限始终是相对于数据分布而定义的。</p><p><strong>期望范围</strong>。较弱但更紧密的仍然是“预期”的界限。这些界限是在重量/数据集中提出期望值后保持的界限：</p> <span><span class="mjpage mjpage__block"><span class="mjx-chtml MJXc-display" style="text-align: center;"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbb E[G_n(f_w)] < \epsilon."><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">e</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">[</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">g</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.06em;">f</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">w</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">]</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">&lt;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><p>与通常保留到通常保留到数据的权重和概率边界的统一边界不同，期望边界在更相等的基础上处理权重和数据。</p><p><strong>结合边界</strong>。考虑到这些选择，可以混合和匹配。由于这些操作是非共同的，因此您可以将订单交换以使界限加倍。改变了基本概率分布的选择，不同的概括范围的可怕范围进一步增长。为了简化问题，通常可以以一种格式将界限转换为另一种格式。</p><h2>命名的界限</h2><p>关于如何和绑定什么的选择的许多特定选择具有专用名称。不幸的是，这些名称既不详尽也不是一致。</p><p>一些更重要的：</p><ol><li><strong>均匀收敛</strong>：概率上的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="G_n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">g</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>在绘制数据集的概率上，并<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="w \in\mathcal W"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">在</span></span><span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-