概念衡量模型类表达噪声的能力。如果您的模型类可以适应更多的噪音，那么它会更加复杂。</p><h3> VAPNIK-CHERVONENKIS（VC）维度</h3><p>我们将从最著名的模型级复杂度度量开始：VC维度。这要求我们返回二进制分类。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/eopg27lxqn7txkyiqlby" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/qoi6dzpu2ljnb5vbg3io 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/wbo9cspw84d35wxf408d 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/pepz7ubh1ioeazk0j1da 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/fvgoixgg6ks2xtnccuro 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/biqmb1zrhhz1kp6a9bo1 500w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/ynvkjgokvfzdsq9wkxg5 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/oanhi0vurllacqwmvxwa 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/prfgoi6im1w7rhsinjum 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/wwwyaimfnjlbhsrblar8 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uG7oJkyLBHEw3MYpT/lc4o35wshiu2wdxgphzb 927w"><figcaption>几个模型类别的决策边界。在每种情况下，所描述的决策边界是一组无限的合适决策边界之一。重要的一点是，至少存在一个这样的决策界限，从而在任何随机标记上都可以进行完美的分类。</figcaption></figure><p>我们首先定义<strong>增长函数</strong>，这是模型类可以对任意输入集<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="(x_1, \dots, x_m) \in \mathcal X^m"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-sup" style="font-s